16:20.960 --> 16:23.960
'Well, not here, you won't. Revenge is a cup of coffee...'

16:23.960 --> 16:25.480
..best served cold.

16:25.480 --> 16:27.960
- 'Goodbye, David.' No, no, wait. 
- Zack...

16:30.960 --> 16:32.320
Fuck!

16:33.960 --> 16:34.960
Oh, just piss off!

